Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.81,0:00:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.21,0:00:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.22,0:01:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.42,0:01:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到好事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.44,0:01:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剃毛解除不能被丈夫看到\N为了婚外情对象无阴毛羞耻插入小穴性受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.18,0:01:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.32,0:01:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.92,0:01:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.60,0:01:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.07,0:01:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给您拖鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.20,0:01:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是半年前认识的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.20,0:01:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成工作项目之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丈夫意外的把同事带回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.16,0:02:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人也来喝一杯吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子\N怎么打算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.44,0:02:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊\N真子有点怕生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有恶意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子\N拿啤酒过来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.58,0:02:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.32,0:02:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.13,0:02:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他倒点啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.94,0:03:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.15,0:03:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.05,0:03:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气\N家务我拿手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了\N没关系交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.07,0:04:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不擅长与人交流的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道该怎么办好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.01,0:04:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人\N盘子放哪里呢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.35,0:04:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N总觉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉\N想在电视里看到的剧情的预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.64,0:04:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我不太会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉就会变成这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.82,0:05:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N可能是着期待的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N让我很为难呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里开始了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每月数回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐瞒着丈夫\N我们偷前的见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认生的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.06,0:06:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被丈夫束缚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N被丢掉的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉完全对丈夫不忙的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了解压的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪念的拍摄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会给别人看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.72,0:07:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过这样的照片\N总觉得会生什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.46,0:07:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是常有的事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.86,0:07:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总感觉没有拒绝的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.75,0:07:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感觉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.42,0:07:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N好羞涩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请允许我剃毛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.53,0:08:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丈夫最近性爱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怎么性爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.54,0:08:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思就是说\N性生活不和谐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.63,0:09:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杯子给你\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们平凡的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天相同的时间段\N重复着相同事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.53,0:09:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到老一直这样的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们干杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.21,0:09:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N身体去往了另一个方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.48,0:09:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要个孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.95,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男女\N喜欢哪个呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.35,0:10:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩也不错呢\N我开始觉得危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.34,0:10:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣脱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股往前点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劈开大点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.31,0:11:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱动的话会受伤呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剃干净了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.95,0:14:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己看看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.03,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羞涩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.63,0:14:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过于羞涩\N不好意思看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不太一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己拿着\N好好的看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腿部抬高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.34,0:15:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能砍到吗?
