Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.60,0:36:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:00.30,0:38:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天过着平常的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:02.97,0:38:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.72,0:38:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定\N我们还是分开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:30.47,0:38:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.74,0:38:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.43,0:39:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.17,0:39:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:10.91,0:39:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:12.38,0:39:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下啊\N我说真姊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:14.11,0:39:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N发简讯真稀奇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.05,0:39:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给妈妈发简讯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.18,0:39:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样啊\N妈妈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.45,0:39:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈有什么事情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:24.12,0:39:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.66,0:39:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来啊\N我们一起喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.26,0:39:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈有什么事情呢\N说清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:33.06,0:39:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.53,0:39:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:36.67,0:39:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.00,0:39:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\N我们喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:42.14,0:39:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:43.34,0:39:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道婚外情很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.54,0:39:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说\N过于刺激了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:50.95,0:39:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:03.95,0:41:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请允许我脱毛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:11.29,0:41:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丈夫性生活不和谐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:18.50,0:41:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,添加了婚外情的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:24.77,0:41:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法告诉丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:27.04,0:41:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们的秘密啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.94,0:43:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:03.14,0:43:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然进来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.14,0:43:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着什么急呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:09.01,0:43:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:11.15,0:43:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:12.88,0:43:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们性爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:16.75,0:43:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉爽吧\N看的很清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:22.89,0:43:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是生理日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:25.83,0:43:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:27.56,0:43:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无所谓呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.30,0:43:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:50.98,0:44:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:53.38,0:44:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得明早叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:33.46,0:50:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:57.88,0:50:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.97,0:51:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:02.21,0:52:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着丈夫出门工作的\N中午时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:07.15,0:52:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们来点刺激的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:10.89,0:52:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚外情对像这样说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:16.95,0:53:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在拍摄吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:21.76,0:53:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在没有穿内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:35.64,0:53:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在便利商店的厕所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:06.60,0:54:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴湿哒哒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:34.35,0:56:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在得好爽了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:49.96,0:56:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自慰小穴变得湿哒哒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:29.20,0:57:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:28.46,0:58:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:32.60,0:58:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊\N打开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:18.91,0:59:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:02.69,1:00:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N停止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:06.69,1:00:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续下去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.98,1:00:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站好啊
