Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:26.36,1:03:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:55.78,1:04:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:57.65,1:04:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要继续了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:56.24,1:05:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要继续了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:13.19,1:06:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:12.72,1:07:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要继续了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:56.42,1:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要继续了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:19.11,1:09:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N停止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:25.52,1:09:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
