Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:36.92,1:10:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新播放看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:11.09,1:11:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:14.83,1:11:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么在一起？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:18.43,1:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外面偶尔遇都的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:20.70,1:11:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟朋友去购物的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:22.97,1:11:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:25.11,1:11:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的机会\N说是一起吃饭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:27.37,1:11:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正打算给你电话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:30.31,1:11:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:49.13,1:11:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:50.86,1:11:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差不多要回去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:54.07,1:11:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不过瘾啊\N继续喝酒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:57.40,1:12:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怀疑我的妻子\N婚外情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:00.74,1:12:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.28,1:12:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有点担心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:05.41,1:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是真的吧\N对吧 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:16.89,1:12:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏家庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:18.76,1:12:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会婚外情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:21.03,1:12:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:27.17,1:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:28.64,1:12:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈应该不是婚外情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:32.51,1:12:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:34.64,1:12:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:36.78,1:12:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多喝点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:43.32,1:12:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子\N喝点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:47.45,1:12:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来喝点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:52.93,1:12:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N破坏家庭的过程是很开心的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:57.06,1:12:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚外情的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:58.27,1:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的啊\N差不多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:01.20,1:13:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对真子感情很深\N没有那种感觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:08.41,1:13:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:10.68,1:13:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真开心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:11.88,1:13:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们感情很好的对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:19.49,1:13:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啤酒给我\N拿过来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:24.29,1:13:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以选择吗?\N请
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:03.80,1:14:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:05.13,1:14:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我习惯了这样的场景呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:46.91,1:14:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丈夫睡着了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:20.20,1:16:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:39.69,1:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋了吧\N这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:31.07,1:17:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:32.94,1:17:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徹志人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:36.01,1:17:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就就回去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:38.01,1:17:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:40.95,1:17:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再喝点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:43.88,1:17:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:46.29,1:17:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要早超呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:48.02,1:17:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:49.89,1:17:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早点休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:00.43,1:18:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天什么日子知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:02.97,1:18:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:04.17,1:18:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N记得住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:08.04,1:18:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N我们去哪里玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:13.51,1:18:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:30.33,1:18:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很享受的样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:37.67,1:18:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是有妻子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:51.95,1:18:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的肉棒不喜欢吗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:33.45,1:21:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丈夫的肉棒\N相比如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:38.65,1:21:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肉棒更加的好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:18.22,1:23:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:01.86,1:24:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:05.73,1:24:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:17.61,1:24:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔舔干净啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:52.45,1:24:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天跟丈夫出门
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:56.58,1:24:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:59.79,1:25:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他着急回家了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:02.99,1:25:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是\N今天带妻子出去吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:08.60,1:25:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:28.75,1:25:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:38.22,1:25:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丈夫马上就回来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:45.97,1:25:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:47.43,1:25:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他马上就回来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:52.11,1:25:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:53.04,1:25:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N请回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:13.99,1:26:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:18.80,1:26:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:36.42,1:26:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N马上就回来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:55.77,1:26:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不唷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:02.31,1:27:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:05.11,1:27:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体好热呢
